    "endLabelIds": "",
    "endLabelNames": "",
    "title": "2024年京东开放平台换签续费公告",
    "followRuleId": "1370012045359955968",
    "content": "<p class=\"sl-paragraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">尊敬的商家朋友：</span></p><p class=\"sl-paragraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">自2024年1月1日起，京东开放平台商家可于京麦后台自主操作换签续费，详细流程如下：</span></p><p class=\"sl-paragraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">一、适用范围</span></strong></span></p><p class=\"sl-paragraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">未签署长期合同或适用平台使用费的京东开放平台商家（含企业店及个人/个体店）。</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">已签署长期合同商家，如需换签会另行公告告知，请以最新公告为准。</span></span></p><p class=\"sl-paragraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">二、换签续费标准</span></strong></span></p><p class=\"sl-paragraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">商家经营的店铺不得出现以下任意一项情形：</span></span></p><p class=\"sl-paragraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">（一）店铺资质不符合《</span><a style=\"color: blue; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=2614\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #0563c1;\">京东开放平台招商资质标准细则</span></a><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">》或资质过期而未及时补全、更新的（资质查询路径：京麦PC端-店铺管理-品牌管理/经营资质）。</span></span></p><p class=\"sl-paragraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">（二）违反《京东JD.COM开放平台在线服务协议》需停止<strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">提供店铺服务或终止合作的情形。</span></strong></span></p><p class=\"sl-paragraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">三、换签续费流程</span></strong></span></p><p class=\"sl-paragraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">未签署长期合同或适用平台使用费的商家须按以下流程完成换签续费：</span></p><p class=\"sl-paragraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">（一）商家换签：</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">若商家未签署长期合同，可于2024年1月1日起在京麦后台进行新合同的确认及签署。新合同签署生效后，按照新合同执行。</span></span></p><p class=\"sl-paragraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">（二）店铺续费：</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">完成合同换签的商家，应依照与京东签署的相关协议及</span><u><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #4472c4;\">《</span></u><a style=\"color: blue; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=638209647311982592&amp;btype=1\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #4472c4;\">京东开放平台类目资费规则</span></a><u><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #4472c4;\">》</span></u><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">完成店铺费用的缴纳。</span></span></p><p class=\"sl-paragraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">四、&nbsp;换签续费时效</span></strong></span></p><p class=\"sl-paragraphCxSpLast\" style=\"text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">商家需要在当前合同有效期内<strong>（2024年3月31日前）</strong>完成换签续费操作，如逾期未完成，京东有权停止提供店铺服务或终止合作。</span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormalCxSpFirst\" style=\"text-align: right; line-height: 2;\" align=\"right\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">京东</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormalCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-align: right; line-height: 2;\" align=\"right\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">2023</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">年12月18日</span></span></p>",
